Storage layout
--------------
```
user_root_dir/
  <project>/
    <name>/
      runs/
        <run_id>/
          meta.json
          status.json
          summary.json
          events.jsonl
          logs.txt
          media/
```

Legacy layout is also supported for backward compatibility:

```
./.runicorn/
  runs/
    <run_id>/
      ...
```
 
Notes
-----
- GPU telemetry is shown if `nvidia-smi` is available.
- Windows compatible.


